{"tid":127241,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人明白睇住人小圈子自己又無得出聲果隻感覺","createTime":"2017-02-20T03:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T13:36:52.000Z","uid":68111,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4d9ee423c0604dc651a14a9137e40d7a869d2c84","tid":127241,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:24:16.000Z","msg":"本來係一堆人黎，但係連自己都唔知點解既原因就會開始比人小圈子<br />\n日日見面食飯，咩都係一堆人做，但係自己就好似多餘左出黎<br />\n最弊係四年都唔會有機會轉第二班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇住佢地係自己面對細細聲講野，自己都已經知道唔可以哄埋去聽<br />\n但係唔癡住班人會project 無谷，啲圈子上年已經定曬型咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直都未扯爛層皮，但係自己就已經好似一個人咁<br />\n果隻無力感有無人明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999 同 too long"},{"pid":"e91ccbe3e152be3df5bb859fbc86ee816cf03af2","tid":127241,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:25:43.000Z","msg":"啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e34bee286c39b827e796398072c7111633aee91c","tid":127241,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:26:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啱乜"},{"pid":"7e31d1ae62d39d6043346e4301e18e91622f451a","tid":127241,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:27:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啱乜</blockquote><br />\n你講得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d12374abcfdd3f296872d12ff81386f1ffdb085","tid":127241,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:27:27.000Z","msg":"啱for 1999"},{"pid":"49282b9f734