hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實本來已經好鐘意講野嫁啦&hellip; 平時講野又還好既佢地都會應<br />\n就係成日都會無端端堆左一堆堆咁講野，你都唔知道佢地講緊乜又笑咁&hellip;"},{"pid":"d2d375114f5c915678456692233de1e4695efc3a","tid":127241,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T03:45:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我明 但成個圈子得我係男仔<br />\n佢地就日日傾韓劇化妝買衫乜乜乜<br />\n我完全加入唔到話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吓你果陣點堆呢個埋嫁"},{"pid":"f4927e0ab729afc587610e4f20916c9c94225f53","tid":127241,"uid":56763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:02:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f37ad3699dde3119cfcfbfd6b0f77e3809e1f8","tid":127241,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aac787a86149966ea14065509ad0b15fa670889","tid":127241,"uid":22820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:19:55.000Z","msg":"岩啊 最憎小圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71b942f9b3262d212e9a798fa1ba85259d5c3ba","tid":127241,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩啊 最憎小圈子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平胸都要比人小圈子?"},{"pid":"2453dad0e9ca0d4b8be2b25dc993cf1cd86